Interface DualListbox

  • All Superinterfaces:
    utam.core.framework.base.PageObject, utam.core.framework.base.UtamBase
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DualListboxImpl
    public interface DualListbox
extends utam.core.framework.base.PageObject
    Selector: lightning-dual-listbox Represents the lightning-dual-listbox Lightning web component. Get the label text, the selected label text, the source label text, or an error message associated with the dual list box. Check if there's an error, or if the field is required. Click the source item or the selected item. Get the selected options and the source options. , created from JSON resources/utam/lightning/dualListbox.utam.json
